@database "RxMUIHelp"
@author Alfonso Ranieri

@Node "Main" "RxMUIHelp"

    @{b}RxMUIHelp@{ub}
    Copyright © 2000-2004 Alfonso Ranieri


    @{" Author " LINK "Author"}  @{" WRID " LINK "WRID"}


    @{fg fill}RxMUIHelp@{fg text} is a little tool to obtain help information from
    RxMUI classes.

    RxMUIHelp may only be used from a shell.

    @{fg fill}RxMUIHelp@{fg text} template is:

    @{fg shine}CLASS/M/A,SUPER/S,OA=ONLYATTRS/S,OM=ONLYMETHODS/S,QUICK/S@{fg text}

    - @{fg shine}CLASS@{fg text}
      one or more arguments describing what you want to obtain
      help for; they are RxMUI class names

    - @{fg shine}SUPER@{fg text}
      a switch keyword to include super class attributes and
      methods

    - @{fg shine}ONLYATTRS@{fg text}
      a switch keyword to only print out attributes

    - @{fg shine}ONLYMETHODS@{fg text}
      a switch keyword to only print out methods

    - @{fg shine}QUICK@{fg text}
      a switch keyword to print out non verbose information

@EndNode

@EndNode

